    "body": "## Summary\n\n- Add MistralLarge3 to the model list that auto-enables FlashInfer AllReduce Fusion on supported single-node multi-GPU deployments.\n- Also handle wrapper configs whose outer architecture differs from the text backbone: `mistralai/Mistral-Small-4-119B-2603` loads as `PixtralForConditionalGeneration`, while the text backbone is `MistralLarge3ForCausalLM`.\n- Add tuned FP8 MoE config files for the targeted Mistral path.\n- Leave the explicit disable flag respected after model-specific auto-adjustments.\n\n## H200 Validation\n\nEnvironment:\n- Host/container: `ion8-h200`, `sglang_bbuf`\n- Device: NVIDIA H200\n- Code under test: PR head `2eac31917e940dfd616169de3e8bdf4b87854af3`\n- Model: `mistralai/Mistral-Small-4-119B-2603`, snapshot `86caf1b82960d2b0fa735f6f169e13d589b00fd6`\n- Download status: full checkpoint downloaded into the Hugging Face cache; cache footprint is about `226G`.\n\nValidation passed:\n\n```bash\nPYTHONPATH=python python3 -m py_compile python/sglang/srt/server_args.py\npre-commit run --files python/sglang/srt/server_args.py\n```\n\nReal model server-args check after downloading the checkpoint:\n\n```text\nouter architecture: PixtralForConditionalGeneration\ntext architecture:  MistralLarge3ForCausalLM\nTP size:            4\nenable_flashinfer_allreduce_fusion: True\n```\n\nThis confirms the PR-specific auto-enable path is active for the actual downloaded model on H200, not only for a mocked causal-LM config.\n\n## H200 GSM8K Accuracy Comparison\n\nEnvironment:\n- Host/container: `ion8-h200`, `sglang_bbuf`\n- Devices: 4x NVIDIA H200, `CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=2,3,4,5`\n- Code under test: PR head `2eac31917e940dfd616169de3e8bdf4b87854af3`\n- Model: downloaded `mistralai/Mistral-Small-4-119B-2603`, snapshot `86caf1b82960d2b0fa735f6f169e13d589b00fd6`\n- Server: TP4, BF16, FP8, `--load-format mistral`, `--chat-template mistral`, `--disable-cuda-graph`, `--max-total-tokens 8192`\n- Eval: `sglang.test.run_eval`, `gsm8k`, completion API, `num_shots=8`, `max_tokens=512`, `temperature=0.0`\n- Samples: requested `num_examples=1400`; evaluated `1311` examples after reserving the 8 few-shot examples.\n\nComparison:\n\n| Mode | Accuracy | Delta vs off | Latency | Output throughput |\n| --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: |\n| FlashInfer AllReduce Fusion off (`--enforce-disable-flashinfer-allreduce-fusion`) | `0.9153318078` | `0.0000000000` | `464.330 s` | `357.132 tok/s` |\n| FlashInfer AllReduce Fusion on (PR auto-enable path) | `0.9138062548` | `-0.0015255530` | `436.554 s` | `379.976 tok/s` |\n\nThe GSM8K accuracy delta is `-0.15 pp` (2 examples out of 1311), while the same run shows higher output throughput with the fusion path enabled. This indicates no material accuracy regression from the auto-enabled FlashInfer AllReduce Fusion path in this H200 FP8 TP4 setup.\n\nCommand shape:\n\n```bash\nCUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=2,3,4,5 \\\nPYTHONPATH=python \\\nSGLANG_JIT_DEEPGEMM_FAST_WARMUP=true \\\npython3 -m sglang.launch_server \\\n  --model-path /root/.cache/huggingface/hub/models--mistralai--Mistral-Small-4-119B-2603/snapshots/86caf1b82960d2b0fa735f6f169e13d589b00fd6 \\\n  --served-model-name mistral-small4-fp8-pr24611 \\\n  --load-format mistral \\\n  --trust-remote-code \\\n  --tp 4 \\\n  --dtype bfloat16 \\\n  --quantization fp8 \\\n  --mem-fraction-static 0.80 \\\n  --max-total-tokens 8192 \\\n  --disable-cuda-graph \\\n  --chat-template mistral \\\n  [--enforce-disable-flashinfer-allreduce-fusion for the off run]\n\npython3 -m sglang.test.run_eval \\\n  --base-url http://127.0.0.1:<port> \\\n  --model mistral-small4-fp8-pr24611 \\\n  --eval-name gsm8k \\\n  --api completion \\\n  --max-tokens 512 \\\n  --num-examples 1400 \\\n  --num-threads 512 \\\n  --num-shots 8\n```\n\n## Correctness Smoke\n\nCommand shape:\n\n```bash\nCUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=2,3,4,5 \\\nPYTHONPATH=python \\\nSGLANG_JIT_DEEPGEMM_FAST_WARMUP=true \\\npython3 -m sglang.bench_one_batch \\\n  --model-path /root/.cache/huggingface/hub/models--mistralai--Mistral-Small-4-119B-2603/snapshots/86caf1b82960d2b0fa735f6f169e13d589b00fd6 \\\n  --model-config-parser mistral \\\n  --load-format mistral \\\n  --trust-remote-code \\\n  --tensor-parallel-size 4 \\\n  --dtype bfloat16 \\\n  --quantization fp8 \\\n  --mem-fraction-static 0.80 \\\n  --max-total-tokens 4096 \\\n  --disable-cuda-graph \\\n  --correctness-test \\\n  --output-len 8 \\\n  --cut-len 4\n```\n\nResult:\n- Loaded the FP8 model successfully with TP4; each rank reported `type=PixtralForConditionalGeneration, quant=fp8`.\n- FlashInfer workspace initialized successfully for ranks 0-3 with backend `trtllm`.\n- Correctness-test prefill/decode completed successfully.\n\n## H200 Benchmark\n\nBenchmark command shape:\n\n```bash\nCUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=2,3,4,5 \\\nPYTHONPATH=python \\\nSGLANG_JIT_DEEPGEMM_FAST_WARMUP=true \\\npython3 -m sglang.bench_one_batch \\\n  --model-path /root/.cache/huggingface/hub/models--mistralai--Mistral-Small-4-119B-2603/snapshots/86caf1b82960d2b0fa735f6f169e13d589b00fd6 \\\n  --model-config-parser mistral \\\n  --load-format mistral \\\n  --trust-remote-code \\\n  --tensor-parallel-size 4 \\\n  --dtype bfloat16 \\\n  --quantization fp8 \\\n  --mem-fraction-static 0.80 \\\n  --max-total-tokens 8192 \\\n  --cuda-graph-bs 1 4 \\\n  --batch-size 1 4 \\\n  --input-len 512 \\\n  --output-len 16\n```\n\nWarmed comparison, same H200 box, same downloaded checkpoint:\n\n| Mode | Batch | Prefill throughput | Median decode throughput | Overall throughput | Total latency |\n| --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: |\n| FlashInfer AllReduce Fusion off | 1 | 7648.43 tok/s | 211.46 tok/s | 3810.25 tok/s | 0.1386 s |\n| FlashInfer AllReduce Fusion on | 1 | 8080.64 tok/s | 208.42 tok/s | 3885.46 tok/s | 0.1359 s |\n| FlashInfer AllReduce Fusion off | 4 | 5369.37 tok/s | 708.78 tok/s | 4463.04 tok/s | 0.4732 s |\n| FlashInfer AllReduce Fusion on | 4 | 5404.22 tok/s | 702.33 tok/s | 4502.25 tok/s | 0.4691 s |\n\nThe warmed H200 run shows no throughput regression in the tested setup:\n- Batch 1 overall throughput: `3810.25 -> 3885.46 tok/s` (`+1.97%`).\n- Batch 4 overall throughput: `4463.04 -> 4502.25 tok/s` (`+0.88%`).\n\nNote: on this H200 environment, the runtime searched for `triton_3_6_0/E=128,N=512,device_name=NVIDIA_H200,dtype=fp8_w8a8*.json` MoE configs and fell back to defaults, so the added MoE config files are not exercised by this specific H200 benchmark.\n\n## Validation\n\n- Downloaded and validated the full `mistralai/Mistral-Small-4-119B-2603` checkpoint on H200.\n- Real-model `ServerArgs._handle_model_specific_adjustments` check with TP4.\n- GSM8K accuracy comparison, fusion off vs fusion on, on 1311 examples with 8-shot prompting.\n- FP8 TP4 correctness smoke test with FlashInfer AllReduce Fusion enabled.\n- FP8 TP4 warmed benchmark with FlashInfer AllReduce Fusion enabled and explicitly disabled.\n- `PYTHONPATH=python python3 -m py_compile python/sglang/srt/server_args.py`\n- `pre-commit run --files python/sglang/srt/server_args.py`\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!-- pr-states:start -->\n---\n### CI States\n\nLatest PR Test (Base): <!-- slot:pr-test:start -->[Run #25987594135](https://github.com/sgl-project/sglang/actions/runs/25987594135)<!-- slot:pr-test:end -->\nLatest PR Test (Extra): <!-- slot:pr-test-extra:start -->:warning: **Not enabled** — add `run-ci-extra` label to opt in.<!-- slot:pr-test-extra:end -->\n<!-- pr-states:end -->\n",
